  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study of safety and efficacy of ceftaroline fosamil in Subjects with Staphylococcus
      aureus Bacteremia or with Methicillin-Resistant Staphylococcus aureus (MRSA) Bacteremia
      persisting after at least 72 hours of vancomycin and/or daptomycin treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Subjects with either S. aureus bacteremia or persistent MRSA bacteremia will be treated with
      open label ceftaroline fosamil, safety will be monitored and clearance of bacteremia will be
      evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
